metadata.name: Head Of Knowledge
metadata.description:
This is the last project from the artist formerly known as Didi.  
Didi produced collections such as Didi's Pieces and Abundant Abstractions. It is time to hang up the title of Didi and move into a new identity and path. Here are the last 111 pieces by Didi. Thank you to everyone who supported the journey of Didi and believed from the start. Didi sends his utmost love and gratitude from the grave. I now present to you " Death Of Didi."
